node.title: Stay in your homes: Armed offenders squad, police negotiation team at serious Napier incident
node.description: "There are cordons in place and residents are asked to stay in their homes as a precaution."
node.content: ["Residents are asked to stay inside as police attend a serious incident in Gilray Avenue, Maraenui, Napier.", "\"Armed offenders squad (AOS) and police negotiation team (PNT) are in attendance,\" a spokesperson says.", "\"There are cordons in place and residents are asked to stay in their homes as a precaution.\"", "More to come."]
